These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, tea
2 different pets are kept: pony, dog
1. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
2. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Beverage   | tea  | juice |
| Pet       | pony | dog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: peas, strawberry
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, surfing
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3
2. the person eating strawberry is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Food   | peas | strawberry |
| Sport      | surfing     | golf  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
2 different pets are kept: lizard, guinea-pig
There are 2 different nationalities: french, nigerian
1. the french is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the french is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Pet   | lizard | guinea-pig  |
| Nationality   | french | nigerian |

